'''Richard Douglas "Rick" Hurst''' (born January 1, 1946) an [[United States|American]] actor who portrayed Deputy [[Cletus Hogg]], [[Boss Hogg]]'s cousin, in the 1980 to 1983 seasons of ''[[The Dukes of Hazzard]]''.<ref name="imdb">[http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0403647/ Rick Hurst at the Internet Movie Database] </ref>
Hurst has also appeared in many movies, including ''[[The Karate Kid, Part III]]'' (1989) as the Announcer. He is the father of fellow actor [[Ryan Hurst]].<ref name="imdb"/>
